Kulig (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Lyakhlinsky Selsoviet, Khivsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Kulig is located 23&nbsp;km north of Khiv (the district's administrative centre) by road. Vertil is the nearest rural locality.
